Messages.Value: Thank you for calling the travel agency, this is Isabella. How may I assist you today?
Yes, I'm calling because I had a flight delay that caused me to miss my connecting flight. And now I'm stuck in a hotel room with no transportation to get to my destination.
I'm so sorry to hear that. Can I have your name and booking number please?
My name is John Smith and my booking number is 123456789. My origin city was Chicago and my destination is New York City.
Thank you for that information, John. I apologize for any inconvenience this delay has caused you. Let me check on your flight status and see what I can do to help.
It's been over 24 hours now and I'm still not on another flight. I can't believe how terrible your service has been.
I understand your frustration, John. I will do my best to assist you and get you to your destination as soon as possible. Please bear with me while I look into this further for you.
I've been waiting for hours on hold and I haven't received any updates. This is completely unacceptable!

I apologize for any inconvenience this has caused you, John. I will do my best to expedite the process and get you the information you need. In the meantime, is there anything else I can help you with?
No, I just want to get to my destination. This has been a nightmare!
